video.title: Good Witch
video.synopsis: Raising her daughter in the small town of Middleton, an enchanting widow with magical powers provokes the interest and exasperation of a big-city doctor.

episodes.synopsis: When recently divorced doctor Sam and his teenage son Nick move in next door to Grey House, Cassie and Grace hasten to make them feel welcome.
episodes.title: Starting Over … Again

episodes.synopsis: While Cassie and Sam are still having trouble seeing eye to eye, Grace gets caught up in Nick's shenanigans and is accused of stealing.
episodes.title: Apologies and Remembrances

episodes.synopsis: Cassie tries to help a frightened young woman who seeks refuge at Grey House. The residents of Middleton gear up for the Heritage Festival 10K race.
episodes.title: Running Scared

episodes.synopsis: The search is on for Cassie's mysteriously departed guest. Nick confides in Grace. Ryan's ex attends the Heritage Ball, leading to a confrontation.
episodes.title: Do the Right Thing

episodes.synopsis: When Cassie's troublemaking cousin Abigail appears, Cassie must stay on her toes as Abigail catches Sam's eye and brings out Grace's rebellious side.
episodes.title: All in the Family

episodes.synopsis: Cassie is on edge concerning Abigail's activities in Middleton, fearing her cousin is stirring up trouble. Grace and Nick begin to find middle ground.
episodes.title: The Truth About Lies

episodes.synopsis: As an epic blizzard is poised to hit Middleton, Cassie worries about an expectant couple staying at Grey House, sensing trouble with the pregnancy.
episodes.title: The Storm

episodes.synopsis: While a storm pummels the town, Cassie and Sam tend to Eve's husband, Brian, who's suddenly ill. Grace, Nick and Anthony are stuck in the library.
episodes.title: Together We Stand …

episodes.synopsis: While Cassie struggles with the notion of possibly losing her shop, Sam deals with an unexpected visit from his ex-wife, Linda.
episodes.title: Homecoming

episodes.synopsis: Struggling to keep her shop, Cassie gets unexpected support. As Cassie helps Sam deal with Linda, she realizes her feelings for Sam have changed.
episodes.title: True Colors

episodes.synopsis: As all of Middleton gears up for its annual Halloween festival, a mysterious guest who checks into Grey House threatens to ruin the frivolity.
episodes.title: Something Wicked, Part 1

episodes.synopsis: While Cassie deals with the furtive new guest in Grey House, Grace asks for help dealing with school bullies who are accusing her of being a witch.
episodes.title: Something Wicked, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Just as Cassie ponders more than friendship with Sam, Linda tries to reconcile with him. Meanwhile, Grace anxiously prepares for her driving test.
episodes.title: Second Time Around

episodes.synopsis: An old college friend of Cassie's threatens to derail her relationship with Sam, and Linda interferes when Grace asks Sam to teach her to drive.
episodes.title: Driven

episodes.synopsis: Linda and Sam lock horns over Nick, and Ryan unexpectedly returns to town, prompting Cassie to wonder if any romance is right for her.
episodes.title: Out of the Past

episodes.synopsis: Sam helps Grace move through her grief over her father, Linda moves in and drives Nick to distraction, and Cassie learns the truth about John.
episodes.title: Trouble with Love

episodes.synopsis: Cassie faces conflicting feelings over Sam and John, Grace's internship goes a little too well, and Nick picks a surprising extracurricular activity.
episodes.title: Surprise Me

episodes.synopsis: Grace helps a co-worker get her confidence back, Sam ponders letting Nick study abroad, and Cassie vacillates between Sam's and John's affections.
episodes.title: Risk

episodes.synopsis: Cassie plans a surprise party for Martha, but the townsfolk make keeping the secret a challenge. Meanwhile, Sam weighs a job offer from the hospital.
episodes.title: What's Your Secret

episodes.synopsis: Cassie lands in a pickle when a rumor reaches John that she is planning a romantic dinner for him. Meanwhile, she helps Sam with a big decision.
episodes.title: Truth

episodes.synopsis: As the Lights Festival gets underway, Sam and Cassie share a moment of connection at the lake house that takes them both by surprise.
episodes.title: A Perfect Match, Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Lights Festival needs Cassie's help to stay illuminated, and Grace witnesses a surprise that puts her in an awkward position.
episodes.title: A Perfect Match, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: When a popular novelist comes to stay at the Grey House, Cassie may end up being more help than the romance writer ever imagined.
episodes.title: The Enchantress Unites, Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Middleton’s new guest makes a professional decision. Cassie comes to a realization about Sam while bringing the town together for a special event.
episodes.title: The Enchantress Unites, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: As everyone awaits its blooming, the Middleton Merriwick has a curious effect on the women in town. Grace senses some interest from Nick.
episodes.title: A Budding Romance

episodes.synopsis: A friend from Abigail's past arrives at the Grey House. Ben follows a sudden urge to get the old Middleton Theater back in operation.
episodes.title: Without Magic for a Spell

episodes.synopsis: Cassie decides magic is the best solution when two guests at the Grey House get off on the wrong foot. Sam has trouble planning a perfect date.
episodes.title: Day After Day

episodes.synopsis: Cassie recommends an old romance film to Ben for the Middleton Theater's opening night. Martha runs into some trouble with the town budget.
episodes.title: How to Say, 'I Love You!'

episodes.synopsis: When an anxious chef comes to town, Cassie suggests a recipe designed to put her at ease. Grace receives a special gift for her birthday.
episodes.title: A Birthday Wish

episodes.synopsis: A jealous Abigail thinks selling Venezuelan chocolates might be the key to competing with Cassie's popularity. Nick has a falling out with Noah.
episodes.title: Say It with Candy

episodes.synopsis: A new paintbrush goes a long way for a reticent traveling artist in Middleton. Cassie involves Sam in her annual planning of a health event.
episodes.title: In Sickness and in Health

episodes.synopsis: Cassie plans a surprise to celebrate the anniversary of Sam's arrival. Grace's magically arranged meetings with Noah don't go quite as expected.
episodes.title: Somewhat Surprising

episodes.synopsis: Cassie finds a curious young girl playing in the Grey House gardens. Sam's visiting sister acts a bit odd. Martha makes an exciting announcement.
episodes.title: Not Getting Married Today, Part 1

episodes.synopsis: As their parents get swept in planning for the big day, Michael and Vanessa just about reach their limit. Cassie gets some unexpected news about Sam.
episodes.title: Not Getting Married Today, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: At Cassie's urging, some ancient, spooky relics are unearthed at city hall, while Middleton prepares for its annual Halloween celebrations.
episodes.title: The Halloween Prophecy, Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The predictions of the ancient Perriwood Curse seem to be coming to fruition in a very mysterious and eventful Halloween for Middleton.
episodes.title: The Halloween Prophecy, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Sam hunts for the perfect ring to give Cassie for their engagement, although she's technically already accepted his marriage proposal.
episodes.title: With This Ring

episodes.synopsis: Previously lost sheet music composed by famed 1930s Middleton songwriter Jacob Heyward is discovered in an old piano bench at Grey House.
episodes.title: In 4/4, with Emotion

episodes.synopsis: Hoping to make amends, Abigail's father appears in Middleton. Cassie counsels an expectant couple. Grace questions her love of math.
episodes.title: Daddy's Home

episodes.synopsis: Cassie and Sam encounter a few obstacles when they take Grace and Nick to a lake house for a weekend getaway with their soon-to-be family.
episodes.title: Family Time

episodes.synopsis: Inspired by a trunk full of vintage clothes that belonged to Cassie's ancestor Elizabeth Merriwick, Grace discovers a love of storytelling.
episodes.title: Written Like a Merriwick

episodes.synopsis: Grace schemes to get Nick and her friend Katie together in time for a dance, while a dating website developer checks in at Grey House.
episodes.title: Match Game

episodes.synopsis: Sam travels to Colombia to assist during a disaster, causing Cassie to consider their mortality. Grace uncovers more of Middleton's history.
episodes.title: Til Death Do Us Part

episodes.synopsis: After Grace discovers a letter describing Elizabeth Merriwick's wedding dress, Cassie sets out to find her ancestor's beautiful antique gown.
episodes.title: All Dressed Up

episodes.synopsis: Cassie and Sam attend eye-opening bachelor and bachelorette parties. Grace gathers the women of Middleton to make a special quilt.
episodes.title: How to Make a Middleton Quilt

episodes.synopsis: Abigail's romance fizzles but she gets a new job as mayor, while everyone prepares for the wedding of Cassie and Sam, only six days away.
episodes.title: Tossing the Bouquet

episodes.synopsis: On the eve of Middleton's bicentennial Halloween festival, a ruby of historical importance gets stolen. Abigail has a rough start as the new mayor.
episodes.title: Tale of Two Hearts, Part One

episodes.synopsis: Romance takes a turn for the worse after the Heart of Middleton ruby is stolen -- but Cassie has a prime suspect in a visitor to Grey House.
episodes.title: Tale of Two Hearts, Part Two

episodes.synopsis: Sam tries to find the legendary tree where Cassie's ancestors were married while Abigail considers handing mayoral duties back to Martha.
episodes.title: The Forever Tree Part One

episodes.synopsis: Middleton celebrates as Cassie and Sam's wedding day arrives while Sam and Grace continue seeking the Forever Tree. Abigail makes a surprising ally.
episodes.title: The Forever Tree Part Two

episodes.synopsis: During their honeymoon, Cassie and Sam help save a vineyard. Martha auditions for a TV role. Nick goes ghost hunting at Grey House with a friend.
episodes.title: The Honeymoon

episodes.synopsis: Royalty comes to Grey House. Sam is visited by an ailing friend. Grace starts an internship at City Hall. Stephanie weighs her romantic options.
episodes.title: The Prince

episodes.synopsis: College acceptance time proves challenging for Grace and Nick. Sam tries to teach a resident better bedside manners. Abigail dates a former nemesis.
episodes.title: The Tea

episodes.synopsis: Cassie and Grace visit a college where the former is receiving an honor and the latter counsels her homesick host. Martha starts broadcasting gossip.
episodes.title: The Road Trip

episodes.synopsis: The Tinsdales vacation at Grey House. Abigail meets Donovan's mother, who thinks the couple is cursed. The ex-fiancé of Stephanie's boyfriend visits.
episodes.title: The Grey-cation

episodes.synopsis: Martha finds the town's long-lost charter -- with a treasure map. Grace discovers Luke's secret agenda. Adam helps Stephanie with her food truck launch.
episodes.title: The Treasure

episodes.synopsis: Middleton's residents wish on a comet. Sam is offered his dream job. Grace prepares her valedictorian speech. Donovan tries to win Abigail back.
episodes.title: The Comet

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Martha continue hunting for treasure and make an unexpected find. Grace discovers a passion for fashion. Nick prepares to depart for college.
episodes.title: The Graduation

episodes.synopsis: Cassie's college roommate makes an unexpected visit. Sam's plans for a romantic Halloween are repeatedly thwarted.
episodes.title: Curse from a Rose Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The town rallies to break Blairsville's pumpkin-carving record. Autumn still harbors resentment from the past.
episodes.title: Curse from a Rose Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Sam frets about finding the perfect anniversary present for Cassie. A guest at Grey House seems highly interested in the Merriwicks.
episodes.title: The Anniversary

episodes.synopsis: While helping Joy plant a tree in memory of her mother, Cassie uncovers a time capsule buried by Grace many years ago. Sam competes in a chili cook-off.
episodes.title: The Chili

episodes.synopsis: At an estate sale, Joy hopes to buy an antique clock for Martha's renovation project. Stephanie's ex-husband Wes pays a surprise visit.
episodes.title: The Clock

episodes.synopsis: After receiving a mysterious letter, advice columnist Martha speculates about which couple will soon experience heartbreak during a progressive dinner.
episodes.title: The Dinner

episodes.synopsis: Cassie pursues a temporary job as an art professor. Sam diagnoses Adam's condition. Abigail and Donovan uncover more clues that may help break the curse.
episodes.title: The Mandala

episodes.synopsis: Sam performs surgery on Adam. Joy believes she had a dream foretelling a big breakup and tries to stop it from coming true.
episodes.title: The Dream

episodes.synopsis: To celebrate Grey House's 225th anniversary, Cassie displays Nathaniel Merriwick's paintings, inspiring Martha to direct a tableau vivant.
episodes.title: The Tableau

episodes.synopsis: Cassie hosts a chocolate festival at Grey House, which gives Joy an opportunity to use the family recipe for a magical confection.
episodes.title: The Chocolates

episodes.synopsis: Cassie brings the women of her book club on an eventful road trip to Chicago. Sam's new boss Grant continues making his job difficult.
episodes.title: The Loft

episodes.synopsis: Ahead of Martha's housewarming gala in Middleton, a final clue leads to a fateful reunion – and the resolution to an ancient curse.
episodes.title: The Bird

episodes.synopsis: Things don't go as planned for Cassie and Sam's romantic date night and Abigail and Donovan's engagement party. Joy has a mysterious dream.
episodes.title: The Party

episodes.synopsis: Cassie and Sam go on a double date with Grant and his girlfriend. Martha puts together a "Grease"-themed movie night in the park.
episodes.title: The Shell

episodes.synopsis: Martha plans a baby shower for her daughter-in-law, Claire. Abigail gets an offer to sell her shop. Stephanie starts taking French lessons.
episodes.title: The Delivery

episodes.synopsis: Joy revives a defunct Middleton tradition as Sam's surgery on a famous basketball player is thrown into limbo.
episodes.title: The Exchange

episodes.synopsis: Joy's recurring dreams inspire the cousins to go in search of a missing piece from her past. Martha experiences a strange series of events.
episodes.title: The Kite

episodes.synopsis: The cousins toss coins into Middleton's wishing well, producing surprising results. Sam reunites with a high school classmate who is now a rock star.
episodes.title: The Wishes

episodes.synopsis: Cassie and Sam visit his ailing sister. Abigail faces unanticipated competition. Adam considers returning to his old job at the hospital.
episodes.title: The Magic

episodes.synopsis: Sam wants to return to work. Stephanie vies for admission to an academy in Paris. Joy grows concerned over Zoey's job as a firefighter.
episodes.title: The Sprint

episodes.synopsis: When the cousins' powers act strangely, Sam recruits help to find a missing amulet at Grey House. A couple takes the next step in their relationship.
episodes.title: The Search

episodes.synopsis: In the series finale, the Merriwicks mystery unravels as the lives of other Middleton residents take meaningful turns.
episodes.title: The Wedding
